Conversion:
 |-+-------+--+--------------------+------|
   +-STRIP-+  +-B2C----------------+
              +-B2D----------------+ (4)
              +-B2X----------------+ (4)
              +-C2B----------------+
              +-C2D----------------+
              +-C2F----------------+ (3)
              +-C2I----------------+ (3)
              +-C2P-+------------+-+ (3)
              |     +-(2)(scale)-+ | (3)
